{"tid":1553722,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【蘋果fact check】《鏗鏘集》炒晒車！ 太子站仍有3人「被消失」","createTime":"2019-09-08T16:43:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-09T23:11:39.000Z","uid":226548,"like":25,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"9dfc3db02a5e3391272b59a0c8114aeac98b3264","tid":1553722,"uid":226548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T16:43:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/vdo/20190908/720pix/1567879352_1646.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2Fvdo%2F20190908%2F720pix%2F1567879352_1646.jpg&h=7d3cc091&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>【逆權運動】《鏗鏘集》未解太子站疑團 仍有3名傷者「被消失」</strong><br />\n<br />\n8.31港鐵太子站警察無差別打人事件，消防處救護員最初報告有10名傷者，但後來只有7人送院，外界質疑為何有3人「被消失」。<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">消防多番解釋最初點算有錯</span></strong>，7人才是正確數字。港台節目《鏗鏘集》昨天（7日）在Facebook專頁亦報道，當日有3名傷者坐港鐵列車到油麻地站後才送院，似乎填補了已消失的3人。不過，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">《蘋果》翻查影片，發現消防處救護員進入太子站內點算傷者前，該列列車早已駛走並抵達油麻地站</span></strong>，意味<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">《鏗鏘集》所指的3人，並非外界所關注「被消失」的3人。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n但如上文所述，載着3名傷者的「屍殺列車」在救護員首次點算人數前，早已離開太子站並抵達油麻地站。換言之，救護員最初在太子站點算到10名傷者時，不可能包括《鏗鏘集》提及的3人，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">意味「被消失」的3名傷者，仍然只能以「消防點算錯誤」解釋。</span></strong>若要釐清當晚太子站有多少名傷者，或要待港鐵公布CCTV才知悉真相。"},{"pid":"a129fd00fc8fc66a05ed84bed8868efb427bdb19","tid":1553722,"uid":226548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T16:43:56.000Z","msg":"Source:<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190908/60021654\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190908%2F60021654&d=h%2B0F1AfFk4MBaO73S6qK%2BqjD3B6m7wr0JF9t5bmmazk%3D&h=960ae9e5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190908%2F60021654&h=874dd43c\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.